Privacy Policy
Privacy Statement
This privacy policy governs your use of the software application Geography Quiz, created by Vladimir Bayatov. The app is a quiz that allows you to check your knowledge of flags of different world countries.
What information does Geography Quiz obtain and how is it used?
Geography Quiz will request access to data such as the following:
- Your Game Center Nickname
- Your quiz scores
Geography Quiz uploads that data to the server which stores it and is used for the global leaderboard where users of Geography Quiz can see Game Center Nicknames and quiz scores of other users of Geography Quiz.
Does Geography Quiz collect precise real-time location information of the device?
No, Geography Quiz does not collect precise information about the location of your mobile device.
Do Third Parties See or Have Access to Information Obtained By The Application
Other users of Geography Quiz can see your Game Center Nickname and your quiz scores on a global leaderboard.
What are my opt-out rights?
You may uninstall the app at any time using the standard iOS app uninstall process.
Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the new Privacy Policy at this URL (http://learzing.com/policy9.html). You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes.
Your Consent
By using Geography Quiz, you consent to the processing of your information as set forth in this Privacy Policy.
